dct_title_s: Vniverse Europe maritime eiusque navigationis descriptio = Generale Paschaerte van Europa, soe verre die Zeecusten ende Navigatien streckende zÿn
dct_alternative_sm: Universe Europe maritime eiusque navigationis descriptio
dct_description_sm: gepractizeert doer Lucas Iansz Wagenaer van Enchuusen ; Ioannes à Doetecum, F.
Bar scale on map given in "Duÿtzsche mÿlen."
Decorative cartouches and border, coats of arms.

Appears in Waghenaer's Spieghel der Zeevaerdt, Leiden:Christophe Plantin, 1584-1588.
